<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<kml xmlns="http://www.opengis.net/kml/2.2">
<Document>
  <name>五台山 2 天古建深度(佛光寺+南禅寺朝圣)</name>
  <description></description>
  <Folder>
    <name>D1 北京 → 五台山(台怀镇)</name>
    <description>约 360km · 5h · 五爷庙+显通寺+塔院寺</description>
    <Placemark>
      <name>D1 行程连线</name>
      <Style><LineStyle><color>ff3539E5</color><width>3</width></LineStyle></Style>
      <LineString><tessellate>1</tessellate><coordinates>116.659905,40.129109,0 115.506183,38.850787,0 113.600528,39.008153,0 113.596393,39.009694,0 113.59597,39.008315,0 113.600029,39.009154,0 113.600528,39.008453,0</coordinates></LineString>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>1. 顺义枫泉花园</name>
      <description><![CDATA[北京顺义出发 · 6:30 走京昆高速 G5 · 约 360km · 早出发保时间<br/><br/>标签: start<br/>坐标(GCJ-02): 116.659905, 40.129109<br/>高德导航: <a href="https://uri.amap.com/navigation?to=116.659905,40.129109,%E9%A1%BA%E4%B9%89%E6%9E%AB%E6%B3%89%E8%8A%B1%E5%9B%AD&mode=car&src=wutaishan">点这里导航</a>]]></description>
      <Style><IconStyle><color>ff00C853</color><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/pushpin/ylw-pushpin.png</href></Icon></IconStyle></Style>
      <Point><coordinates>116.659905,40.129109,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>2. 保定服务区</name>
      <description><![CDATA[京昆高速中段休整 · 9:00 · 约 130km<br/><br/>标签: service<br/>坐标(GCJ-02): 115.506183, 38.850787<br/>高德导航: <a href="https://uri.amap.com/navigation?to=115.506183,38.850787,%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%9A%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%8C%BA&mode=car&src=wutaishan">点这里导航</a>]]></description>
      <Style><IconStyle><color>ff1976D2</color><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/pushpin/ylw-pushpin.png</href></Icon></IconStyle></Style>
      <Point><coordinates>115.506183,38.850787,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>3. 五爷庙(广化寺)</name>
      <description><![CDATA[求财最灵 · 香火最旺 · D1 下午首站 · 必去 0.5<br/><br/>标签: attract<br/>坐标(GCJ-02): 113.600528, 39.008153<br/>高德导航: <a href="https://uri.amap.com/navigation?to=113.600528,39.008153,%E4%BA%94%E7%88%B7%E5%BA%99%28%E5%B9%BF%E5%8C%96%E5%AF%BA%29&mode=car&src=wutaishan">点这里导航</a>]]></description>
      <Style><IconStyle><color>ffFF6F00</color><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/pushpin/ylw-pushpin.png</href></Icon></IconStyle></Style>
      <Point><coordinates>113.600528,39.008153,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>4. 显通寺</name>
      <description><![CDATA[五大禅处之首 · 青铜殿(明万历)+ 铜塔 + 无量殿(国内唯一青铜建筑群) · 必去 0.7<br/><br/>标签: attract<br/>坐标(GCJ-02): 113.596393, 39.009694<br/>高德导航: <a href="https://uri.amap.com/navigation?to=113.596393,39.009694,%E6%98%BE%E9%80%9A%E5%AF%BA&mode=car&src=wutaishan">点这里导航</a>]]></description>
      <Style><IconStyle><color>ffFF6F00</color><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/pushpin/ylw-pushpin.png</href></Icon></IconStyle></Style>
      <Point><coordinates>113.596393,39.009694,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>5. 塔院寺</name>
      <description><![CDATA[五台山标志性大白塔(高 56.4m · 释迦牟尼舍利塔 · 尼泊尔风格) · 必去 0.6<br/><br/>标签: attract<br/>坐标(GCJ-02): 113.59597, 39.008315<br/>高德导航: <a href="https://uri.amap.com/navigation?to=113.59597,39.008315,%E5%A1%94%E9%99%A2%E5%AF%BA&mode=car&src=wutaishan">点这里导航</a>]]></description>
      <Style><IconStyle><color>ffFF6F00</color><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/pushpin/ylw-pushpin.png</href></Icon></IconStyle></Style>
      <Point><coordinates>113.59597,39.008315,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>6. 寿宁寺素斋</name>
      <description><![CDATA[台怀镇寿宁寺素斋 · 17:30 时段 · 11:30 也开 · 错过吃不上<br/><br/>标签: food<br/>坐标(GCJ-02): 113.600029, 39.009154<br/>高德导航: <a href="https://uri.amap.com/navigation?to=113.600029,39.009154,%E5%AF%BF%E5%AE%81%E5%AF%BA%E7%B4%A0%E6%96%8B&mode=car&src=wutaishan">点这里导航</a>]]></description>
      <Style><IconStyle><color>ffFFB300</color><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/pushpin/ylw-pushpin.png</href></Icon></IconStyle></Style>
      <Point><coordinates>113.600029,39.009154,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>7. 五台山宾馆</name>
      <description><![CDATA[台怀镇中心 · 老牌国营 · 21:00 入住 · 旺季提前订<br/><br/>标签: hotel<br/>坐标(GCJ-02): 113.600528, 39.008453<br/>高德导航: <a href="https://uri.amap.com/navigation?to=113.600528,39.008453,%E4%BA%94%E5%8F%B0%E5%B1%B1%E5%AE%BE%E9%A6%86&mode=car&src=wutaishan">点这里导航</a>]]></description>
      <Style><IconStyle><color>ff7B1FA2</color><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/pushpin/ylw-pushpin.png</href></Icon></IconStyle></Style>
      <Point><coordinates>113.600528,39.008453,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>
  </Folder>
  <Folder>
    <name>D2 佛光寺 + 南禅寺 → 返京</name>
    <description>约 360km · 6h · 国宝中的国宝 + 顺路亚洲最古木构</description>
    <Placemark>
      <name>D2 行程连线</name>
      <Style><LineStyle><color>ffE5881E</color><width>3</width></LineStyle></Style>
      <LineString><tessellate>1</tessellate><coordinates>113.394811,38.870102,0 113.120804,38.702103,0 113.306797,38.40064,0 114.515993,38.040634,0 116.659905,40.129109,0</coordinates></LineString>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>1. 佛光寺</name>
      <description><![CDATA[国宝中的国宝 · 东大殿(唐 857) · 文殊殿(金 1137) · 祖师塔(北魏) · 必去 1.0 · 1961 第一批国保<br/><br/>标签: attract<br/>坐标(GCJ-02): 113.394811, 38.870102<br/>高德导航: <a href="https://uri.amap.com/navigation?to=113.394811,38.870102,%E4%BD%9B%E5%85%89%E5%AF%BA&mode=car&src=wutaishan">点这里导航</a>]]></description>
      <Style><IconStyle><color>ffFF6F00</color><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/pushpin/ylw-pushpin.png</href></Icon></IconStyle></Style>
      <Point><coordinates>113.394811,38.870102,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>2. 南禅寺</name>
      <description><![CDATA[中国现存最古木构(782 唐建中三年) · 17 尊唐代塑像 · 佛光寺南 5km 顺路 · 必去 0.8<br/><br/>标签: attract<br/>坐标(GCJ-02): 113.120804, 38.702103<br/>高德导航: <a href="https://uri.amap.com/navigation?to=113.120804,38.702103,%E5%8D%97%E7%A6%85%E5%AF%BA&mode=car&src=wutaishan">点这里导航</a>]]></description>
      <Style><IconStyle><color>ffFF6F00</color><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/pushpin/ylw-pushpin.png</href></Icon></IconStyle></Style>
      <Point><coordinates>113.120804,38.702103,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>3. 京昆高速服务区</name>
      <description><![CDATA[返京途中 · 11:30 · 约 200km 处大休整<br/><br/>标签: service<br/>坐标(GCJ-02): 113.306797, 38.40064<br/>高德导航: <a href="https://uri.amap.com/navigation?to=113.306797,38.40064,%E4%BA%AC%E6%98%86%E9%AB%98%E9%80%9F%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%8C%BA&mode=car&src=wutaishan">点这里导航</a>]]></description>
      <Style><IconStyle><color>ff1976D2</color><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/pushpin/ylw-pushpin.png</href></Icon></IconStyle></Style>
      <Point><coordinates>113.306797,38.40064,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>4. 石家庄午餐</name>
      <description><![CDATA[京昆高速石家庄段下高速 · 13:00 · 当地家常菜<br/><br/>标签: food<br/>坐标(GCJ-02): 114.515993, 38.040634<br/>高德导航: <a href="https://uri.amap.com/navigation?to=114.515993,38.040634,%E7%9F%B3%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%84%E5%8D%88%E9%A4%90&mode=car&src=wutaishan">点这里导航</a>]]></description>
      <Style><IconStyle><color>ffFFB300</color><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/pushpin/ylw-pushpin.png</href></Icon></IconStyle></Style>
      <Point><coordinates>114.515993,38.040634,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>5. 顺义枫泉花园</name>
      <description><![CDATA[抵京 · 17:00 · 全程约 720km<br/><br/>标签: end<br/>坐标(GCJ-02): 116.659905, 40.129109<br/>高德导航: <a href="https://uri.amap.com/navigation?to=116.659905,40.129109,%E9%A1%BA%E4%B9%89%E6%9E%AB%E6%B3%89%E8%8A%B1%E5%9B%AD&mode=car&src=wutaishan">点这里导航</a>]]></description>
